  sectionId (37823)
  sectionNo (1)
  orderNo 1
  title `Short title and commencement.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_1_content
  footnotes `1. 6th June, 2007, vide notification no. S.O. 943(E), dated 4th June, 2007, see Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part II, sec. 3(ii).`
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_18_21_00012_200723_1517807327001&sectionId=37823&sectionno=1&orderno=1&orgactid=AC_CEN_18_21_00012_200723_1517807327001
obj_root_law_sections_1_content:
  string
  line `(1) This Act maybe called the National Rural Employment`
  line `Guarantee (Extension to Jammu and Kashmir) Act, 2007.`
  line
  line `(2) It shall come into force on such date^1`
  line `as the Central Government may, by notification in the`
  line `Official Gazette, appoint; and different dates may be appointed for different areas in the State and any`
  line `reference to the commencement of this Act shall be construed as a reference to the coming into force of`
  line `that Act in such areas.`
obj_root_law_sections_2:
  sectionId (37824)
  sectionNo (2)
  orderNo 2
  title `Extension and amendment of the National Rural Employment Guarantee Act, 2005.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_2_content
  footnotes `*. Vide notification No. S.O. 3912(E), dated 30th October, 2019, this Act is made applicable to the Union territory of Jammu and Kashmir and the Union territory of Ladakh.`
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_18_21_00012_200723_1517807327001&sectionId=37824&sectionno=2&orderno=2&orgactid=AC_CEN_18_21_00012_200723_1517807327001
obj_root_law_sections_2_content:
  string
  line `(1) The`
  line `National Rural Employment Guarantee Act, 2005 (42 of 2005) (hereinafter referred to as the principal`
  line `Act) and all rules, orders and schemes made thereunder by the Central Government are hereby extended`
  line `to, and shall be in force in, the State of Jammu and Kashmir*.`
  line
  line `(2) With effect from the date of commencement of this Act, in the principal Act, in sub-section (2) of`
  line `section 1, the words "except the State of Jammu and Kashmir*" shall be omitted.`
obj_root_law_sections_3:
  sectionId (37825)
  sectionNo (3)
  orderNo 3
  title `Construction of reference to a law not in force in Jammu and Kashmir.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_3_content
  footnotes `*. Vide notification No. S.O. 3912(E), dated 30th October, 2019, this Act is made applicable to the Union territory of Jammu and Kashmir and the Union territory of Ladakh.`
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_18_21_00012_200723_1517807327001&sectionId=37825&sectionno=3&orderno=3&orgactid=AC_CEN_18_21_00012_200723_1517807327001
obj_root_law_sections_3_content:
  string
  line `Any reference in any`
  line `Act mentioned in the principal Act to a law which is not in force in the State of Jammu and Kashmir* shall,`
  line `in relation to that State, be construed as a reference to the corresponding law, if any, in force in that State.`
